Command: cast [three spell words] at [target]
         cast offensive [sp boost]
         cast stop

Arguments:
  [sp boost] is the amount of spellpoints used to increase damage
  [three spell words] are the words needed to cast a spell
  
Examples:
  cast exs fla blt at guard         Fire bolt (Mages)
  cast chl xfr min at guard         Drain health (Clerics)
  cast offensive 45	            Set your offensive spell boosting to 45
			 	    spellpoints for more damage (default is 40)

See 'help spellcasting' for how to cast spells.
